{"tid":2308554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息違限聚令和口罩令等定額罰款增至一萬元","createTime":"2020-12-02T03:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T05:42:25.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"022050bdc479cefa71740c92c17a5e29cd1e3333","tid":2308554,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指行政會議同意，違反限聚令和口罩令等定額罰款增至一萬元。<br />\n<br />\n消息指考慮到二千元的定額罰款，對部分富有人士未能起阻嚇作用，參考外國違反限聚令罰款比香港重，行政會議同意將現時違反限聚令、口罩令及不遵從強制檢測的定額罰款，由二千元增加至一萬元，以提高阻嚇力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415041&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2YLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=1dbb9e0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415041&h=4c4ed51e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415041</a>"},{"pid":"314fcaaf6d16364c61a08e237af17f07c31403d5","tid":2308554,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9af7b8847cf7255dd455658ed9cb6627de251dd","tid":2308554,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"Old news is so exciting<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff9bce6dd0b29f552a23e0b9aee6fbf8dc61d0d","tid":2308554,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"找班狗一次過包住成條彌敦道 逐個抄 咪回到血囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb3ba4757f11fdf4116a987dedbacde579ddaf9","tid":2308554,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"所有機組人員及船員在機場入境時，強制留下深喉唾液樣本做測試。不過，措施仍有漏洞，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">到內地出席股東會的上市公司董事、在廣東省設有生產線的公司僱員、與履行與政府相關運作的政府人員和符合相關條件的仲裁員等<span class=\"blue\">仍獲豁免接受病毒測試</span></span></strong></span>，未能杜絕相關輸入個案風險。<br />\n許樹昌亦指，第三波爆發與早前放寬邊境措施，容許特定人士豁免檢疫有關，&ldquo;機組人員同海員，或者公務、商務人士，以往這些人在香港都不需要留樣本，而他們很可能將病毒帶入社區&rdquo;。"}]}